item.description: Proshop As of April 2nd the Campus Tennis Centre Pro Shop will close, however, I will still provide a wide range of products for tennis throughout the summer. Joe Cambareri and I will take care of all your stringing needs and provide quick reliable service. Below is a list of all Wilson, Prince and Tecnifibre products. Please email me for prices. Latest Wilson Demo Racquets Latest Wilson/Prince racquets Wilson/Prince tennis shoes Wilson tennis bags Tennis accessories and clothing Wilson tennis balls and ball hoppers
